		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />At the cost of a lot of ROM space. DRW is already strapped for space: <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=14412" class="postlink">The grandpa says what?</a><br /><br />For swinging the heroine's arm, you could do a few rapidly ascending notes on pulse or noise, with the first and last frames quieter than the rest. Play around with <a href="https://pineight.com/nes/#sfxed" class="postlink">my sound effects editor</a> for a while to get a feel for what's possible.

		

		</td>
